The kitchen is equipped with upper and lower cabinets, countertop, sink, faucet, oven, ceramic hob, and extractor hood.&amp;#13;&amp;#13;&#13;&#13;
The hot water system operates through a common aerothermal installation to reduce energy consumption. Additionally, there is a ducted air conditioning system for heating and cooling.&amp;#13;&amp;#13;&#13;&#13;
Bathrooms include white vitrified porcelain sanitary fixtures, wall-mounted sinks, flat shower trays, and chrome faucets. The terraces have water outlets with taps.&amp;#13;&amp;#13;&#13;&#13;
The layout includes a master bedroom with an en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet, two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom for them, and a guest bathroom next to the living area.&amp;#13;&amp;#13;&#13;&#13;
The social area integrates living room, dining room, and open kitchen with breakfast bar, connected to the terrace, which has space for outdoor dining and a seating area.&amp;#13;&amp;#13;&#13;&#13;
The property includes private parking, air conditioning, solarium, balcony, and access to a communal pool.

