Around:&amp;#13;&amp;#13;&#13;&#13;
The Costa Blanca continues to attract people from all over Europe, and other parts of the world, because it offers a unique quality of life in a beautiful setting on the shores of the Mediterranean Sea, surrounded by mountains and lush vegetation.&amp;#13;&amp;#13;&#13;&#13;
